                            <comment id="42704" author="pjones" created="Sat, 4 Aug 2012 13:29:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix for 2.1.3&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="42635" author="jay" created="Fri, 3 Aug 2012 00:06:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the root cause of this problem is that we have to set the page as dirty to write a page with vvp_page_sync_io().&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;patch is at: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/3521&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/3521&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;we should have used patch: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/3194&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/3194&lt;/a&gt;, heh.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="42632" author="yujian" created="Thu, 2 Aug 2012 23:45:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The culprits are:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1442&quot; title=&quot;File corrupt with 1MiB-aligned 4k regions of zeros&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1442&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1442&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; llite: cleanup if a page failed to add into cache&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1059&quot; title=&quot;vvp_page_unmap()) ASSERTION(PageLocked(vmpage))&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1059&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1059&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; clio: to not try to discard freeing pages&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-948&quot; title=&quot;Client recovery hang&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-948&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-948&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; clio: add a callback to cl_page_gang_lookup()&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1576&quot; title=&quot;client sluggish after running lpurge&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1576&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1576&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; llite: correct page usage count&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
